{"tid":350491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發有聲] 樓下有男人不斷打小朋友 個小朋友係咁尖叫..","createTime":"2017-08-07T09:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T14:11:49.000Z","uid":111012,"like":105,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49428c361307c800ba5bb77c80ad5df0c41e774e","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"已經錄咗音 呢個男人成日都見到佢<br />\n好似係單親家庭 平時已經好惡 其實已經知道佢會打小朋友好耐 之前係lift都見到佢扯左個小朋友耳仔走<br />\n但係估唔到而家小朋友大個咗少少仲係咁打.. 小朋友而家大概小六小五左右<br />\n我應唔應該報警好<br />\n如果報咗警個小朋友可能要去寄養家庭..本身已經冇媽媽 又冇咗個爸爸 我驚會影響呢個小朋友..<br />\n我用iphone錄咗音 但係唔識整上嚟 有冇巴絲教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ab80c45062ae39d4519a765db6e3cbfb184fb2","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1d90c4d55ffce82e90b180ead48cb4ac2b727f21","tid":350491,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"soundcloud"},{"pid":"e24f0c5724e45e3f671e4aee8ba5f8ff965df44c","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>soundcloud</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/174051_a80a7d1f0aa02c8742c053829a4749eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F174051_a80a7d1f0aa02c8742c053829a4749eb.jpg&h=c38639a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪呢個😵😵😵😵"},{"pid":"36317db77c94f5df491d0e89332ec14a1012b1d4","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6bf5032b7e53f47d482612117e30d23c6eade0e6","tid":350491,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:45:35.000Z","msg":"搵社工lo"},