oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前見到已經好耐啦..個小朋友戈陣仲係啱啱升小一..."},{"pid":"3d9dc2d47e01de5529e06e57fbfc0f622e52b209","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"利申啲鋼琴聲都係樓下 唔係我地屋企人彈<br />\n另外中間有個細佬把聲突入 唔好意思"},{"pid":"c0d23b1d3aa6cc1a97cea57ddb9d6223ce9c13d7","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申啲鋼琴聲都係樓下 唔係我地屋企人彈<br />\n另外中間有我細佬把聲突入 唔好意思</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ebdda6f09e00cf3d350e1fb34f5c02238abda3be","tid":350491,"uid":15739,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"癡線仲唔報警。。。放上黎有咩用"},{"pid":"58770d7efb0e4b8db3f752b30a9af74dcf699194","tid":350491,"uid":105441,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"打左咁多年, 你宜家先出聲?<br />\n香港人有冇咁冷漠啊?<br />\n快D報警啦!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"d8ab0560bd45d0ae83f36b70938b053d3ea9863b","tid":350491,"uid":72498,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"打小朋友既聲好細 定唔知直程我聽錯<br />\n但咁樣好易俾人當小朋友玩先尖叫"},{"pid":"74985da2efc1a12fb87bca92d167339aedaf5fe2","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"落咗去搵看更幫手 應該會摷上去"},{"pid":"e543b37f23ae8f83ca4ea972db4a343f15396a87","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打小朋友既聲好細 定唔知直程我聽錯<br />\n但咁樣好易俾人當小朋友玩先尖叫</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪入唔到..證據不足..?<br />\n其實中間有男人鬧嘅聲 唔知大家聽唔聽到"},{"pid":"b43d114d1953356109246b8c0f23d9f9af63259c","tid":350491,"uid":63452,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"應該<br />\n報警啦<br />\n個細路自己無得逃走，你可以救佢走"},{"pid":"f032d54e34b504aca852e7d98f2520e8622e786b","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打左咁多年, 你宜家先出聲?<br />\n香港人有冇咁冷漠啊?<br />\n快D報警啦!!!!!!!!!!</blockquote><br />\n嗰陣覺得小朋友細 5,6歲<br />\n而且五六年前我都仲係12,13歲 見到都唔係好敢報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849894398a2859c620e71c47d510242a19b02c5b","tid":350491,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"你講到打到咁勁肯定有傷痕啦"},{"pid":"9464983db612acfcb3a1f7a36fda6706e7bdf688","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"看更話叫咗人上去<br />\n有咩通知我或者佢地會自己報警..<br />\n因為而家未知係邊個單位所以需要一啲時間"},{"pid":"63ec67b6cd52bf422a3e9db8d6c951f1b61cdb73","tid":350491,"uid":134129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"屌 唔識教唔好生啦"},{"pid":"869d326984b3bc6215a9609bc0a67444d8cc869a","tid":350491,"uid":32028,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"背景有d咁輕鬆既音樂真係.............."},{"pid":"a3b468e7334ba87a2325e99f006fa80e4fcc5015","tid":350491,"uid":18170,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"報警衰左只係柒一下<br />\n但如果係小朋友真係比人打而你報左警就可以救到個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c1896e475c476be0a1c3f4ba8223791fc4eb3b","tid":350491,"uid":66171,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:11:13.000Z","msg":"打有咩問題<br />\n問題係因咩事打同埋打既程度姐 <br />\n你知唔知係個老豆暴力傾向定抑或係個細路衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99398a64bcde37baf16c01894c0775c6801dcfff","tid":350491,"uid":107382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"報啦屌，唔覺意重手打死左就仆街"},{"pid":"e48f5ceac2192726b3d30e9f65dd91de39aa88d4","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打有咩問題<br />\n問題係因咩事打同埋打既程度姐 <br />\n你知唔知係個老豆暴力傾向定抑或係個細路衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知道 以前間唔中就會聽到個小朋友喊<br />\n本身個老豆都係五十幾歲 老來得子個啲黎<br />\n都幾惡下 冇見過佢笑 成頭白髮<br />\n從來冇見過個小朋友個媽媽 所以我估係單親家庭<br />\ngrad左之後我就忙返工返學 成日都好夜返屋企 所以唔知道佢呢排仲有冇打小朋友<br />\n今日放假點知又是聽到.."},{"pid":"9b0924ec30e8541d34e1a6375182513f9f6ac37f","tid":350491,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"如果你日日俾人咁打法 你都想有人幫你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b2c86b6cc07e2c295f5effe33ec7e89f4d944a","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"！！！！！已報！！！！！"},{"pid":"ffb61c96cc6ccb89562359a3c27cb0c980aa27fd","tid":350491,"uid":2337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fce4280b664e43e16872f06fc1fa844b6f100b","tid":350491,"uid":92772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effd47302264448b8b5bc17aa15191f1f9dca302","tid":350491,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"你有證有據咁報<br />\n冇可能落你<br />\n報啦<br />\nASAP<br />\n叫得咁慘<br />\n分分鐘告埋佢傷人都得"},{"pid":"52d5c1fe13c341e952b4c391bc924c5d13371925","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"警察打咗過嚟 話而家想去了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a346c42f801c2275afc8d329022d69246f4e4a","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察打咗過嚟 話而家上去了解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"32fedbe7f4eb5581c