g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度年中好多人出post但怕尋仇怕麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都驚 但係真係好不安<br />\n唔想自己個心以後見到個細路都過意唔去<br />\n<br />\n就快一個鐘 都仲尖叫緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過聲音細咗好多"},{"pid":"d81db95ff2761f5869d783e9e7160fa0db126e38","tid":350491,"uid":46151,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.komicolle.org/2014-10/1412505854482.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.komicolle.org%2F2014-10%2F1412505854482.jpg&h=dd76219e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本來樓主就係紅毛仔<br />\n而家係出木杉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08a79e1b9b53082c971dcac842b65a3f283a696","tid":350491,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"appreciate 樓主"},{"pid":"3d99c5d2de8a8b9e0601ff694943e61cfe2c41e9","tid":350491,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打有咩問題<br />\n問題係因咩事打同埋打既程度姐 <br />\n你知唔知係個老豆暴力傾向定抑或係個細路衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢度啲小朋友女都媾唔到唔會明,<br />\nbtw,我都唔認同齋打係有用"},{"pid":"538fc16f5cb496837177ad1b29177bd85327965e","tid":350491,"uid":60301,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"完全無喊聲<br />\n淨係咁叫叫左一粒鐘?<br />\n都幾恐怖下"},{"pid":"f304557d0d7b7d89f8a8fa94347ff24bfd8c8441","tid":350491,"uid":17397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"個背景聽住啲咁輕鬆既音樂配埋啲尖叫聲真係格格不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cdb52f25d7c31f6740492ea7d4bafe96f31503","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2