,"tid":350491,"uid":1198,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪真係可以唔俾警察入屋？<br />\n見到個小朋友識入房閂門就即係冇事。。？<br />\n我唔係好明 咁都得嫁咩<br />\n<br />\n我完全有晒錄音 但係佢都唔問我拎<br />\n已經唔係第一次 以前睇住個小朋友比人扯耳仔<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就真係交左貨咩。。。係咪我唔熟悉法律</blockquote><br />\n無搜查令係可以唔俾"},{"pid":"701830fc5b6ee02cde41bee2bc39506056c4cb0a","tid":350491,"uid":95393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"認真問 知唔知佢點打法?"},{"pid":"4374d976b4b90cdf4cb334aee6b8259fe4e4b446","tid":350491,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"有次鄰居罰個小朋友係走廊做功課 連台凳 阻住曬<br />\n報警之後 班黑警上黎同佢老母交流完 就走咗<br />\n個小朋友仍然係出面做到夜晚9點幾 <br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n結論：報警係冇用"},{"pid":"771dfd9254476cd62efd9ef06f769d8a6c930366","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真問 知唔知佢點打法?</blockquote><br />\n親眼見過嘅淨係扯耳仔 用手打佢個頭<br />\n之前周不時會聽到藤條聲 之後個細路喊得好犀利 有次嗌埋救命 即刻落去同保安講 保安話會處理 但係最後唔知佢有冇報警 呢件都係三年前左右"},{"pid":"f5d56467ecbd4e9a1b09cacf89bfbf522cac1390","tid":350491,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆打仔又關你事?</blockquote><br />\n犯法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfe05d18bd156d3e9ebbc8e6ca0444525effffc","tid":350491,"uid":95393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"你最好有圖有片<br />\n放上黎推上報<br />\n記住打格"},{"pid":"28aee0599ed12a709d9f1a6e7346bdf8b438f1ab","tid":350491,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真問 知唔知佢點打法?</blockquote><br />\n親眼見過嘅淨係扯耳仔 用手打佢個頭<br />\n之前周不時會聽到藤條聲 之後個細路喊得好犀利 有次嗌埋救命 即刻落去同保安講 保安話會處理 但係最後唔知佢有冇報警 呢件都係三年前左右</blockquote><br />\n爸爸落去同保安講的 以前細個屋企人已經叫我同細佬儘量避開呢個男人"},{"pid":"957bdc70e49464fa353c35c19fa83818346fb627","tid":350491,"uid":58670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"知邊個單位試吓再email俾社署同cc埋俾黑警，最少alert 咗佢地同留個底，社署一定要覆你。<br />\n<br />\n雖然都可能冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90ab4cf2829732b5fedc0e66c1cf74e9c962b43","tid":350491,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔：細個我老豆用刀斬我都係咁啦，細路仔唔打點教呀</blockquote><br />\n細個我老豆攞把.50 browning射我都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b00f70333986715c97d2a677230c2df0f0af94","tid":350491,"uid":20429,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"細路唔打教唔聽"},{"pid":"b1fefdf9c9379fb886c392f8ecfbf99c3a08665d","tid":350491,"uid":35370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"社工，議員，記者，黑警"},{"pid":"794e3589fe02beed9440e55e85ae3387066a7c38","tid":350491,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登仔：細個我老豆用刀斬我都係咁啦，細路仔唔打點教呀</blockquote><br />\n細個我老豆攞把.50 browning射我都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個我爸拎高射炮描準我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係點叫教仔呀"},{"pid":"2056691852aaaa372028b077b4ea0b29f424da51","tid":350491,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解嗰時冇人黎救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都嗌得好大聲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e8b2ffc0404c44eb65cb445919062eebe4d675","tid":350491,"uid":31884